            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="member">
          <img src="/images/github.png" alt="" /><div class="member-info">
            <div class="member-name">Copilot</div>
            <div class="member-role">Assistant</div>
            <div class="member-background">
              Master of the digital verse and a certified bug whisperer, I coax lines of code into
              elegant symphonies and make pixels dance to the rhythm of innovation.
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="contact-title sub-heading">Contact</div>
      <div class="contact">
        At Kobilica, we're more than just a service provider; we're your partner in the digital
        world, committed to propelling your vision into a digital reality.
        <div class="contact-center">
          Contact us today at
          <div><a href="mailto:kobilica-digital@outlook.com">kobilica-digital@outlook.com</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <style>
      .center {
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 800px;
        padding: 14px;
      }

      header {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 22px;

        .title {
          font-size: 64px;
          font-weight: 700;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          text-align: center;
          margin: 8px 0;
          font-weight: bold;
          border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary);
          margin: 0 0 1px 0;

          &::before,
          &::after {
            content: "";
            flex: 1;
            border-bottom: 10px solid currentColor;
          }

          &::before {
            margin-right: 0.5em;
          }

          &::after {
            margin-left: 0.5em;
          }
        }
      }

      .sub-heading {
        padding: 4px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 1.3;
        text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--focus);
        background-color: var(--primary);
      }

      .heading {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 8px 0;
        font-weight: bold;

        &::before,
        &::after {
          content: "";
          flex: 1;
          border-bottom: 3px solid currentColor;
        }

        &::before {
          margin-right: 0.5em;
        }

        &::after {
          margin-left: 0.5em;
        }
      }
      .about {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;

        img {
          padding: 5px;
          border: 5px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .about-title {
          font-size: 28px;
          font-weight: 700;
        }
      }

      .services-title {
        margin-top: 16px;
      }

      .services {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;

        .service {
          border: 2px solid var(--primary);
          border-radius: 8px;
          width: 100%;

          @media screen and (min-width: 480px) {
            width: 48%;
          }

          @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
            width: 180px;
          }

          div {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.3;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
            color: var(--focus);
            background-color: var(--primary);
          }

          img {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            filter: grayscale(1) sepia(0.2);
          }
        }
      }

      .team {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .member {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        width: 100%;
        gap: 16px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-bottom: 16px;

        @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
          flex-direction: row;
        }

        img {
          display: block;
          width: 150px;
          height: 150px;
          object-fit: contain;
          border-radius: 50%;
          filter: grayscale(1) sepia(0.2);
        }

        .member-info {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          flex: 1;
        }
        .member-name {
          width: 100%;
          font-size: 18px;
          font-weight: 700;
          line-height: 1.3;
          text-align: center;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          color: var(--focus);
          background-color: var(--primary);
          margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .member-role {
          font-weight: bold;
        }
      }

      .socials {
        margin-top: 8px;
        display: flex;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .contact-title {
        margin-top: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .contact {
        padding: 14px 0;
      }

      .contact-center {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 24px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </div>
</Layout>
